## Frontend API Conventions

- **REST calls** go through the Axios `apiClient` (local) or `cloudApiClient` (cloud) instances in `src/api/client.ts`
- **SSE streams** use a custom `streamLocalFetch()` helper (native fetch, not Axios) because Axios does not support streaming
- The local backend base URL is resolved dynamically via `getBaseUrl()` from `src/api/config.ts` (supports Electron IPC or HTTP)
- All cloud API calls pass the JWT token from `useAuthStore` in the request body (not headers), since the local backend proxies them

